{"lemma":"فَواتٌ","slug":"فَواتٌ","root":"ف.#.ت","root_slug":"ف-_-ت","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-_-ت","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34762"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34762","headword_ar":"فَوْاتٌ","root":"fwt","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of 1. (S, * M, &c.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawotN AlfawaAti","text_ar":"مَوْتٌ الفَوَاتِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sudden death:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, O, K:) likewise termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almawotu AlfawaAtu","text_ar":"المَوْتُ الفَوَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almawotu AlfuwaAtu","text_ar":"المَوْتُ الفُوَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAta mawota AlfawaAti","text_ar":"مَاتَ مَوْتَ الفَوَاتِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He died a sudden death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) The Prophet, passing by a leaning wall, quickened his pace; and being asked wherefore he did so, answered,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axaAfu mawota","text_ar":"اَخَافُ مَوْتَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfawaAti","text_ar":"الفَوَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I fear sudden death"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}